      "comment": "BEANCOUNTER (7) attempts another Waratah series after he missed by just a head in a Bathurst heat two back before a 1.4m second in the final at Menangle last week. Won't spend a penny from this draw and if he gets the gaps he could break through. RONZEL SONNY (1) comes here after making up plenty of ground from a back row draw to get the prize by 1.7 metres at his latest appearance at Bathurst. Up in grade so must raise the bar but he is well served by the ace draw. FIRESTORM RED (8) will relish the return to a venue where he has won five of eight visits including all four attempts over this distance. JEWEL HEAVEN (6) draws wide but is racing well so can measure up with even luck.",
